Package: Rlgi
Title: Interface to the Leiden Grid Infrastructure
Date: 2010-12-14
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Willem van Engen <wvengen@nikhef.nl>
Description: This package provides functions for using R with the 
        Leiden Grid Infrastructure distributed computing system.
Depends: snow, XML
SystemRequirements: Requires LGI (LGI_qsub, LGI_qstat, LGI_filetransfer)
Maintainer: Willem van Engen <wvengen@nikhef.nl>
License: GPL
